Every day I have been looking up your uploads to see whether you had uploaded the "Electrical Circuit Analysis"lectures because I knew you were our only hope.You can imagine my delight to finally see these lectures.In the past you have mentioned in all your humility that you just pass on these lectures but let me reiterate what I feel - You dohduhdah are the God of uploading lectures.I thank you once more and remember that whenever I see any of your uploaded lectures I'll say a little prayer for you.
When may I dare ask will you be uploading the "MathTutorDVD -Engineering Circuit Analysis -Vol.2" lectures?I hope it's pretty soon.

Well. indiaman. I thank dohduhdah for his contribution, but I would really truly (from the bottom of my heart) thank another on demonoid that ripped the Engineering Circuit Analysis vol 1 and have been wondering if he will upload vol 2. I only guess that it is the source of dohduhdah? Btw, the original three torrents apparently have the wrong order. So have that in mind ;)

True @raenkae,I should thank the person who uploaded it on demonoid (of which I have no clue) .So I cannot.The second reason is to download from demonoid you have to have an account which I do not.So my true source is dohduhdah.Hence for me he is the real uploader.And hence my thanks goes out to him.But believe me,if I knew who had originally uploaded this anywhere,I would have definitely thanked him too.But doesn't my gratitude for dohduhdah automatically extend to the original uploader also?
I truly hope so indiaman. I really hope so. I have asked him to upload volume 2, so I guess we need to be patient!
Yes, the content comes from demonoid. I have no idea when volume 2 will become available.
